item.title: NEW UPDATE TO DOLPHIN EMULATOR
item.description:
@licaon-kter The current version of Dolphin Emulator on Fdroid is outdated.

The commit link is: https://github.com/dolphin-emu/dolphin/commit/8ecfa537a242de74d2e372e30d9d79b14584b2fb

The direct download link is: https://dolphin-emu.org/download/dev/8ecfa537a242de74d2e372e30d9d79b14584b2fb/

The current F-Droid version of dolphin is: 5.0-15993

The current Google Play Store version of dolphin is: 5.0-16101

Link to F-Droid Dolphin Emulator page: https://f-droid.org/en/packages/org.dolphinemu.dolphinemu/
